  <brief_title>Nifedipine vs Placebo for Maintenance Tocolysis of Preterm Labor.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Nifedipine for the Maintenance Tocolysis of Preterm Labor: Comparison to Placebo in a Prospective, Randomized Double Blind Trial</official_title>
